{"title":"黄河风（歌词）","authors":["禹本愚"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河风（歌词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禹本愚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从天外飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磅礴直入东海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄色是雄厚的沉思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光是耀眼的霓彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你激荡九曲衷肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昭示民族的奔腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拉成万年强弓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将远天迷雾射开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的力量所在！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从云中飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅入我们的胸怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心田永不枯竭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑靥永不衰败。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那皇天后土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把苦难埋于千古；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用波涛的鼓点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩撞崭新的时代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们乘风向着未来！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}